metadata.name: Lovers
metadata.description:
Long exposure analog photo of us having sex. 
Taken: July 2021 

Film being the true essence of the moment.
Light from the scene falling upon silver halides to record the image.

4815 x 4826 JPG file 

First owner of this NFT will be posted the original negative. 
And will be transferred a 3200 dpi raw uncorrected TIFF file.
